high_descs: Turn right and go towards the shelf unit.
Pick up the big knife on the top shelf
Turn right and go to the the fridge, turn right and go to the counter
Slice the lettuce on the counter
Turn left, go forward then then turn right at the stove
Put the knife into the pan on the stove
Turn right, go to the counter
Pick up a slice of lettuce on the counter
Turn left, go forward then then turn right at the stove
Put the lettuce slice into the pan
Take the pan with the lettuce slice and knife
Turn right twice, go towards the door, turn left at the door
Put the pan on the table
anns.task_desc: Slice a lettuce, put it into a pan, take them to the table.

high_descs: Turn right, go to the black stand.
Take the knife from the stand.
Turn right, go to the fridge, turn right, go to the sink.
Cut the lettuce into slices on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn around, go to the oven to the right.
Put the knife in the pan on the stove top.
Turn right, go back to the counter with the lettuce.
Take a slice of lettuce from the counter.
Turn around, go to the oven to the right.
Put the lettuce in the pan on the stove top.
Take the pan from the stove top.
Turn around, go to the door, turn left to the round table.
Put the pan on lower right of the round table.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan with a slice of lettuce on a table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk up to the small black shelving unit.
Pick up the large metal knife with a golden handle.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and continue straight to the head of lettuce on the kitchen counter.
Slice up the head of lettuce with the large metal knife.
Turn around and begin across the room, stop at the oven and turn right.
Place the large metal knife point down in the metal frying pan that is on the stove.
Turn right and walk across the room to the kitchen counter.
Pick up a piece of sliced lettuce.
Turn around and walk back over to the stove.
Place the piece of sliced lettuce in the frying pan with the large metal knife.
Pick up the frying pan with the large metal knife and piece of sliced lettuce in it.
Turn around and begin walking to the door on the other side of the room, stop at the middle of the round black table and turn left.
Place the frying pan with the piece of sliced lettuce and the knife in it onto the round black table.
anns.task_desc: Place a pan with a piece of sliced lettuce plus a metal knife in it on a round black table.
